				</Card>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Founder -->
	<section class="py-20">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
				<div>
					<h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold">Founded by David Flanagan</h2>
					<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-300">
						David Flanagan is a developer advocate, cloud-native expert, and passionate educator who has spent over a decade
						helping developers master complex technologies.
					</p>
					<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-300">
						Frustrated with the state of technical education full of perfect, scripted demos that don't reflect reality
						David started Rawkode Academy to show the messy, authentic process of building with modern technologies.
					</p>
					<p class="text-neutral-300">
